{"tid":2178580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［赴湯杜火］不甘被剝削選擇權既人落蘋果頭版全版廣告","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T17:45:48.000Z","uid":8435,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4c15ed10a648180091400e3d865a0153ff8232","tid":2178580,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108379573919637/posts/305726880851571/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108379573919637%2Fposts%2F305726880851571%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=ad5a7ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108379573919637/posts/305726880851571/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持及分享<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/不甘被剝削選擇權既人落蘋果頭版全版廣告/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%98%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%9D%E5%89%8A%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E6%AC%8A%E6%97%A2%E4%BA%BA%E8%90%BD%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88%E5%85%A8%E7%89%88%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=8df0e5bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/不甘被剝削選擇權既人落蘋果頭版全版廣告/</a><br />\n<br />\n截止日期 29/8/2020 刊登日期：預計7/9/2020<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n希望集合一班悍衞選舉權利既香港人，夾錢在蘋果日報落頭版廣告，向政府及國際清楚表達： <br />\n1，香港人不要委任議會<br />\n 2，依基本法還市民選舉權利，落實真普選，盡快舉行2020立法會選舉 <br />\n3，不應以疫情作擋戰牌阻礙民主選舉進行 <br />\n目標<br />\n蘋果日報頭版費用為港幣拾捌萬元，但眾籌平台需要10%手續費，所以最終目標為港幣贰拾萬元<br />\n希望每人最多夾$100 ，我地唔只需要一個金錢數目，最重要係有幾多人悍衛選舉權！所以請大家高抬貴手唔好夾咁多！🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"63f7176e03d4a223413335060d40f73dc88f2d25","tid":2178580,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b00a1ab263f8cb016ad3a137e1bafd5e3c7d7581","tid":2178580,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f7d2bfa431d8804926eb9381f00937e4a34748ef","tid":2178580,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c